Now Some of you are experiencing problems with the auto cache downloader for 562 loading 602 client/webclient. In this turtorial Il show you how to make the cache actually auto download and work!! Okay so lets Start Difficulty 2/10 for begginers Download this File Here, this is the client, its a completley different one than what you got... http://www.mediafire.com/?rb26te0fixjc6tf Go to qs.java Search For
private static boolean checkRevision()
And under it you should see a directory, Yours maybe something like this
C:/.562_cache_32v4/cacheRevision.txt
Change that to this
C:/562_cache_32v4/cacheRevision.txt
You may ask, Why the hell is he saying that? theyre the exact same!! Well, think twice, thier not. One is .562_cache and the other is just 562_cache without the '.' Infront of the 5. I changed it to this because if it stayed .562 , It would automatically download part of it. dont ask why... It Just Will Now search for
client.downloadCache
You should see something like this
client.downloadCache("http://Revengescape.com", ".562Cachev4.zip","C:/".562_cache_32v4", "562Cache");
Change
("http://Revengescape.com"
too....
http://download843.mediafire.com/2b1iy3ozmpig/zitfdu5riv2acov/562_cache_32v4.zip
Now where it says
"C:/".562_cache_32v4", "562Cache");
Change it too
C:/"562_cache_32v4", "562Cache"
Again without the '.' before the 5. Now close and save the file, and open the file Class_t.java You will see something like this
Class_x.a("C:/.562_cache_32v4/RevengeScapeCache/");
Change the directory to this
("C:/562_cache_32v4/RevengeScapeCache/");
Now Save and compile and your done!! wohoo! :D. (this only works if your client loads 602/608) Now..... download these files (Very small)... http://www.mediafire.com/?9mk1vun5avdwle6 http://www.mediafire.com/?zlccllru0f013ch Now place them in the data file, and overwrite the ones there. Now core/compile the server files and download a 562 loading 602 client here... If you have errors post below... Also im releasing a webclient tutorial soon! Easy for all of you to understand!! :D.[/b]
